# Generated review output + per-project state. The config (config.json,
# config.schema.json) stays tracked; everything below is produced at run time.
# Patterns are scoped to the dir so they do NOT case-insensitively swallow
# commands/review.md on macOS/Windows.
.adverserial-code-review/review-*/
.adverserial-code-review/worktrees/
.adverserial-code-review/cache/
.adverserial-code-review/learnings.json
.adverserial-code-review/last-review.json
